lead_paragraph: Since Hoffenheim last met Bayern Munich in a top-of-the-table clash during their Bundesliga debut season eight years ago, Julian Nagelsmann's side have spent more time battling to stay in the top flight than fighting for a spot in Europe.

headline.print_headline: Hoffenheim Eye Bayern Upset as Leaders Clash
